                                                                                                       1.2
                                                                                                       2020-05-27
Security Target
ePassport configuration of SECORA™ ID S Infineon Applet Collection - eMRTD V1.0



                          6.Terminals authenticated as CVCA or as DV are not allowed to read data in the
                          EF.DG3 and EF.DG4 .




